snippet.title: The Black Eyed Peas Experience - Gameplay trailer, October 2011 [UK]
snippet.description:
Hey Peabodies! Check out the brand new gameplay trailer of The Black Eyed Peas Experience! Coming out on /November 10th in [Europe] for Wii and Kinect/XBox360! #DontStopTheParty
For more information: www.facebook.com/bepexperience
